subject: Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Liu Xiang beat Dayron Robles in a resumption of their hurdling rivalry, and Lerone Clarke upstaged his Jamaican sprint rival Asafa Powell at 60 meters at the Birmingham Grand Prix in England.
